title: VMI snaps road losing streak with 28-21 win over Mercer
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
Al Cobb passed for 391 yards and two touchdowns on Saturday to lead VMI to a 28-21 win over Mercer that snapped a 30-game road losing streak...
